<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #222;">
  <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px; color: #e74c3c;">‚è∞ Your Trial Has Ended</h2>
  <p>Hi <%= garage_name %>,</p>
  <p>
    Your free trial for the <strong><%= plan_name %></strong> plan has ended.
  </p>
  
  <div style="background: #fdf2f2; border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0;">
    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #e74c3c;">Trial Summary:</h3>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li><strong>Plan:</strong> <%= plan_name %></li>
      <li><strong>Price:</strong> <%= price_formatted %> per month</li>
      <li><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold;">Trial Expired</span></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>What happened?</strong><br/>
    Your trial period has ended and no payment method was provided or the payment failed.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Impact on your service:</strong><br/>
    Your garage is no longer visible to drivers searching for MOT services. You won't receive new bookings until you resubscribe.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Want to continue?</strong><br/>
    You can resubscribe anytime to restore full access to all features:
  </p>

  <% if (billing_portal_url) { %>
  <p>
    <a href="<%= billing_portal_url %>" style="background:#e74c3c;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;margin:8px 0;">Resubscribe Now</a>
  </p>
  <% } %>

  <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; padding: 12px; margin: 16px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #856404;">
      <strong>üìä Your Data is Safe:</strong> All your garage information, booking history, and customer data remain intact. You can resubscribe anytime to restore full access.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Need help deciding?</strong><br/>
    Our support team can help you choose the right plan for your garage. Contact us at 
    <a href="mailto:<%= support_email %>"><%= support_email %></a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    We hope you enjoyed your trial and look forward to welcoming you back soon!
  </p>

  <p>Best regards,<br/>
  <strong>The <%= app_name %> Team</strong></p>
</div>
